---
/**
 * Clothing ecomm best practice: persistent promo/trust strip above the fold.
 * Communicates free-shipping threshold, fulfillment speed, and brand promise.
 */
---
<div class="bg-floof-dark text-white text-center text-xs sm:text-sm py-2.5 px-4">
  <p class="font-medium tracking-wide">
    <span class="text-floof-yellow">✦</span>
    Free shipping over $75
    <span class="mx-2 text-white/30">·</span>
    Printed fresh &amp; ships from the US
    <span class="mx-2 text-white/30 hidden sm:inline">·</span>
    <a href="/shipping-returns" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-floof-pink hidden sm:inline">30-day returns</a>
  </p>
</div>
